imdb.plot outline: Xander Corvus. A name that will forever be infamous in rock history. Follow his journey from Xander's modest beginnings in some of the country's slummiest dive bars, the recording studio meltdowns, and sold-out arenas around the world - not to mention all the pussy along the way. Against all odds, Xander Corvus was on top of the world ready to literally rock out with his cock out. Experience Xander's meteoric rise, sequential downfall, and eventual status as rock n' roll legend in this special presentation. There's no passport required but you're in for one hell of a ride on 'ZZ Behind The Cock' - Xander's World Tour!
